{"tid":1601281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5/10 全民感謝日（和理非行動）","createTime":"2019-09-29T03:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T07:57:52.000Z","uid":21545,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"d347fbb60d8275217b65f12290bb781c87a3820d","tid":1601281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:53:31.000Z","msg":"暫時見出面未有下星期行動post 所以有小小建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地日日都要勇武巴打 打生打死唔係辦法 和理非們都可以做嘢去爭取鎂光燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日就去黃絲餐廳幫襯 之後一齊打卡感謝佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用hashtag #realloveHKshop  去集中火力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一來遊行成本太高 好容易俾狗咬或受傷 損兵折將<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二來可以 make noise 作為一種新抗爭手法 吸引傳媒目光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三來 容易做 所有街坊都可以join <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有咩睇法 歡迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想見到大家受傷被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n餐廳list: <a href=\"https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.restart-hk.com%2FShopList.html&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be0x5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=72c1141f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html</a><br />\n<br />\n日期：10月5日 星期六 <br />\n<br />\n時間： 全日<br />\n<br />\n地點： 任一間支持抗爭嘅餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動 ：幫襯 之後打卡#realloceHKshop"},{"pid":"4ba82e354dcf8a214ff06809eac62ea8523bb63c","tid":1601281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31ba91a1100342355af8bfe3f4ae6bd7ecc624c","tid":1601281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"我想食加藤屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a86294eab901b9c5617d987ea83f8b7f24f443c","tid":1601281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"一個人都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955c8e6ff7d02234ee2cf75d1084ef7bc6195c1d","tid":1601281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"我想食珍苑"},{"pid":"e97feaf06e90c72b56c1df001874a062b1cf9cd9","tid":1601281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"我想食新景園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b89ebdb9218e8c9d93dc26fdeba8f3392300c76","tid":1601281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:59:32.000Z","msg":"我想食好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/t